## üìÅ Project Structure

```
AICode/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ src/                    # Core source code
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lexer.py           # ASCII lexer (v1)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lexer_ai.py        # Unicode lexer (v2)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ parser.py          # ASCII parser (v1)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ parser_ai.py       # Unicode parser (v2)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ast_nodes.py       # AST node definitions
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ type_checker.py    # Hindley-Milner type inference
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ compiler.py        # Bytecode compiler
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ bytecode.py        # Bytecode format & instructions
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ vm.py              # Stack-based virtual machine
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ interpreter.py     # Compiler + VM wrapper
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ stdlib_ai.py       # Standard library
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ module_system.py   # Module loading & imports
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ errors.py          # Error handling system
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ tests/                  # Test suite
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ examples/               # Example programs
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ docs/                   # Documentation
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ main.py                 # CLI entry point
```

